Description: 5 tees around the hole. Begin at 6 feet. Made putt: move back 1 feet. Missed putt: move up 1 feet. Drill complete when all tees are at 8 feet. If a putt is holed from 10 feet, pick up the tee.

Title: Great Lag
Description: Putt 10 balls from 12m. Each ball must finish within a 50cm circle of the hole.

Title: Tour Pizza Slice Approach Drill
Description: From 150 meters, hit one shot short right, short left, long right and long left of the target. Each shot has to be in inside 5 meters of the target and in the correct pizza slice and in a row.

Title: Bogey Free Challenge
Description: Play 18 holes from back tess without making a bogey.

Title: Tour All Round Chip Challenge
Description: Hit 3 bunker shots, drop 3 balls in the rough and  drop 3 in the fairway. Every three shots will be one easy, medium and hard shot (in total 3 easy, 3 medium, 3 hard), get 8/9 up and down.

Title: Full Swing Tour Level
Description: Hit three 9 irons to a total of 15 meters of the target, three 6 irons  to a total of 24 meters of the target and three drivers in a row within a 20 meter fairway

Title: Dirty Thirty
Description: Make 30, 5 feet putts in a row. Every putt has to be different.

Title: Ultimate Tour Test
Description: Play 18 holes worst ball and shoot under par
